1. Python with boto3 to automate AWS tasks like starting/stopping EC2 instances. 
import boto3

ec2 = boto3.client('ec2')
ec2.start_instances(InstanceIds=['i-1234567890'])

2. when I need more complex log parsing compared to grep. 
with open("app.log") as f:
    for line in f:
        if "ERROR" in line:
            print(line)

